The flick portraying Emergency days of 1975-77 was opposed by a woman, who claimed to be the biological daughter of Sanjay Gandhi. The apex court said that the plea filed by the woman challenging the Bombay High Court's July 24 judgment was "devoid of merits".
General Dynamics' margins rose to 13.8 percent in the quarter from 13.2 percent a year earlier. The business had revenue of $7.68 billion during the quarter, compared to analyst estimates of $7.76 billion. During the same period in the previous year, the company earned $2.30 EPS. The Brandes Investment Partners Lp holds 2.57 million shares with $61.94M value, down from 3.26M last quarter. Shareholders of record on Friday, July 7th will be issued a $0.84 dividend. This represents a $3.36 annualized dividend and a dividend yield of 1.73%. The ex-dividend date is Wednesday, July 5th. Plante Moran Finance Advsrs Ltd Liability Company has invested 0.16% of its portfolio in General Dynamics Corporation (NYSE:GD). Lazard Asset Management LLC's holdings in General Dynamics Corporation were worth $5,399,000 as of its most recent SEC filing. The correct version of this piece of content can be read at https://www.thestockobserver.com/2017/07/27/caisse-de-depot-et-placement-du-quebec-reduces-stake-in-general-dynamics-corporation-nysegd.html. Royal Bank Of Canada reiterated a "buy" rating and issued a $220.00 price objective on shares of General Dynamics Corporation in a research note on Friday, June 2nd. Zacks upgraded General Dynamics Corporation (NYSE:GD) on Monday, August 31 to "Hold" rating.04/27/2017 - General Dynamics Corporation had its "hold" rating reiterated by analysts at Stifel Nicolaus. Barclays PLC restated an "overweight" rating and issued a $210.00 price objective (up previously from $200.00) on shares of General Dynamics Corporation in a report on Monday, May 1st. Finally, Jefferies Group LLC reaffirmed a "buy" rating and set a $220.00 price objective (up from $200.00) on shares of General Dynamics Corporation in a research note on Friday, April 28th.Based on the latest notes released to investors, 9 analysts have issued a rating of "buy", 5 analysts "outperform", 6 analysts "hold", 0 analysts "underperform" and 0 analysts "sell". The stock has an average rating of "Buy" and an average price target of $204.72.
