Our Company

We are organized into four business groups and each comprises several business units serving different markets.






 







AerospaceThe Aerospace group has a reputation for superior aircraft design, quality, performance, safety and reliability.

 
 Learn More  

 







Combat SystemsThe Combat Systems group is a global leader in tracked and wheeled military vehicles, weapons systems and munitions.

 
 Learn More  

 







IS&TInformation Systems and Technology provides technologies, products and services that address a wide range of secure mobile communication systems.

 
 Learn More  

 







Marine SystemsMarine Systems designs, builds and supports submarines and surface ships for the U.S. Navy.

 
 Learn More  



 



 



 







Doing the Right ThingGD employees are united by our Ethos—our defining moral character as a company. This Ethos undergirds our culture and our commitment to our communities, employees, customers and shareholders. It drives and determines how we do business and informs our commitment to good corporate citizenship, sustainable business practices and community support.
GD’s Corporate Citizenship Approach
 



 

 






